Paper Code: ETCS-257
Paper: Computer Graphics & Multimedia Lab


List of Experiments:


1. Study of Fundamental Graphics Functions

2. Implementation of Line drawing algorithms: DDA & Bresenham's Algorithm

3. Implementation of Circle drawing algorithms: Bresenham's & Mid Point Algorithm

4. Programs on 2D and 3D transformations

5. Program to implement Cohen-Sutherland line clipping algorithm

6. Program to draw Bezier curve

7. Using Flash/Maya perform different operations (rotation, scaling move etc) on objects

8. Create a Bouncing Ball using Key frame animation & Path animation